---
title: Quick Tunisian Beef & Couscous Bowl with Veggies & Roasted Almonds
description: Introduce your tastebuds to the incredible profiles of Tunisian seasoning, a North African spice that really packs a punch. Sitting
on a bed of fluffy couscous, topped with yoghurt and ready in 20 minutes flat, this tender beef bowl delivers massive flavour with
such speed that it's sure to knock your socks off!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
